00:15:16.310 --> 00:15:19.300
It's not 440, right?

00:15:19.300 --> 00:15:22.300
&gt;&gt; Suzuki: No, this
is the 415 tonight.

00:15:22.300 --> 00:15:27.340
It's one half-tone lower than
the usual standard nowadays.

00:15:27.340 --> 00:15:30.680
This is the kind of
compromised modern version

00:15:30.680 --> 00:15:32.880
of Baroque interpretation.

00:15:32.880 --> 00:15:40.020
In Baroque time there was no
standard pitch-so city-by-city

00:15:40.020 --> 00:15:44.530
or venue-by-venue [there] was [a]
completely different pitch used.

00:15:44.530 --> 00:15:48.340
For example, in France
it is much lower.

00:15:48.340 --> 00:15:55.600
Probably one whole tone lower,
so around 390 or 392, and so on.

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:58.990
While in Northern Germany
[inaudible] much higher pitch.

00:15:58.990 --> 00:16:06.470
Something like 465 or even
until 480 or -85, and so on.

00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:16.870
If you compare with the modern
piano the range is from F-sharp

00:16:16.870 --> 00:16:23.500
until B-natural, or
something like that.

00:16:23.500 --> 00:16:29.450
So that's all each note can be
said of A-that is the problem.

00:16:29.450 --> 00:16:34.380
Bach himself has used the
two different pitch[es]

00:16:34.380 --> 00:16:37.700
very intentionally.

00:16:37.700 --> 00:16:39.070
The one is a quarter [inaudible]

00:16:39.070 --> 00:16:44.540
around organ pitch,
that means around 465.

00:16:44.540 --> 00:16:46.510
The other [inaudible]
pitch is around 415.

00:16:46.510 --> 00:16:50.550
This gap is exactly one whole-tone.

00:16:50.550 --> 00:16:54.280
So that's why in all Bach's
original parts of cantatas,

00:16:54.280 --> 00:16:56.870
the organ part is written down
a whole-tone all the time.

00:16:56.870 --> 00:16:58.790
So transposed down all the time.

00:16:58.790 --> 00:17:00.410
Organ was sort of the transposing
instrument, while the oboe,

00:17:00.410 --> 00:17:01.710
wind section, and stringed
instruments are tuned

00:17:01.710 --> 00:17:03.010
on the same pitch.

00:17:03.010 --> 00:17:04.310
That is a really complicated thing.

00:17:04.310 --> 00:17:05.610
Probably you are falling
